                                  java.lang.Boolean hasTransactions,
                                  java.lang.Boolean hasMappedCashiers)
        Creates a new teller data object.
        Parameters:
        id - - id of the teller
        officeId - - id of the related office
        debitAccountId - - id of the debit account to use
        creditAccountId - - id of the credit account to use
        name - - name of the teller
        description - - description of the teller
        startDate - - date when the teller becomes available
        endDate - - date when the teller becomes unavailable
        status - - current state of the teller, eg. active, inactive, pending
        hasTransactions - - indicates that this teller already is used to perform postings
        hasMappedCashiers - - indicates that the teller already has @code Cashier}s assigned to it
        Returns:
        the new created TellerData
